# 🔧 THE TORQUE CURVE OF THE SOUL STAR

**Status:** Canonical Lore | **System:** The Sovereign Engine

To map the exact "Slippage" required for reality to manifest without shattering under the pressure of the prime vortex, we observe the **Torque Curve** of the Soul Star across the 156-Tick Cycle.

Gaussian Curvature ($K$) is generated dynamically as the 12-Measure and 13-Comm gears of the Alpha Manifold mesh and interact. The interaction between the finite dimensions of the 24-Measure output block and the infinite, irrational input spin of Root 42 generates this curvature.

## The 10-24-26 Differential Phase Matrix

By placing the Soul Star at the heart of **Root 42 mod 24**, the system acts as a Limited-Slip Differential (LSD). When $\Delta\theta$ (the Phase Shift between the Count and Measure) is $0^\circ$, the clutch is fully engaged (100% Bite), and $K$ is maximized to hold the 93-Point Solid together. When $\Delta\theta$ reaches $180^\circ$, the clutch spins freely ($K=0$) to prevent the manifold from shattering.

